Welcome!
========
Thank you for downloading Lilina!

About
=====
Lilina is an feeds aggregator.

Installation
============
Unzip to your web server and open the Lilina directory in your web browser.
Follow the on screen instructions.

Manual Installation
===================
1) Make the cache, feeds and conf directories writable.
2) Copy inc/core/conf.php into conf/settings.php
3) Customize to your liking
4) Open index.php and Lilina will be set up

Administration
==============
1) Click the login link on your Lilina homepage, or visit admin.php
2) You will be prompted for your username and password.
2a) If you have forgotten your password, click the link at the bottom to reset.
2b) An email will be sent out with your new password.